The paper presents a deep reinforcement learning-based system for autonomous braking, which involves computer vision, robotics, artificial intelligence, and human-computer interaction. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
